original_title: Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger Final Live Tour 2014
overview: "You'll be surprised when you'll heaaar-! Kyoryuger Final Battle!!"  A live show that was performed across Japan in March and April of 2014, acting as a final farewell for the cast. It comprises two parts: a scripted show part, and a talk show with the cast. The ToQgers also appear in.
title: Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger Final Live Tour 2014
